yeti.environments.csharp
Class YetiCsharpLogProcessor

java.lang.Object
  yeti.YetiLogProcessor
      yeti.environments.csharp.YetiCsharpLogProcessor

public class YetiCsharpLogProcessor
extends YetiLogProcessor

Class that represents a log processor for Csharp. It is a clone of YetiJavaLogProcessor processLog generates test cases in each cell of the array.

Author:
Sotirios Tassis (st552@cs.york.ac.uk)
